"       <td>",
"        <p>",
"         Enteral feeding tubes",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         (Examples: Abbot Nutrition enteral feeding tube; Cook Endoscopy NJFT; Corpak Medical Systems CORFLO tubes; Covidien tubes; Teleflex Medical tubes)",
