"         <li>",
"          Radio opaque markers each cm",
"         </li>",
"         <li>",
"          Weighted tip to allow propulsion into duodenum by peristalsis",
"         </li>",
"         <li>",
"          Magnets to facilitate jejunal placement",
"         </li>",
"         <li>",
"          Suture loops to allow endoscopic placement",
"         </li>",
"        </ul>",
